Listabl.es
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Author:        Juan Uys <opyate@gmail.com>
Date:          2009.07.07
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------


1. Introduction
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

"Lists on the web"

Represent lists of ontologies described using RDF. Eliminate the need for
each and every web-site - be it social, retail, etc - to store lists of data,
e.g. friends list on FaceBook, or books listing on Amazon.

FaceBook will now be able to get your latest friends list from a listabl.es
implementation, either hosted by the users themselves, hosted in the cloud,
or hosted on http://listabl.es

The data will have value to systems, which is the driving force behind the
Semantic Web.


2. Implementation
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2.1 Tech used

Lift

2.2 Created with Maven

mvn archetype:generate -U \
  -DarchetypeGroupId=net.liftweb \
  -DarchetypeArtifactId=lift-archetype-blank \
  -DarchetypeVersion=1.0 \
  -DremoteRepositories=http://scala-tools.org/repo-releases \
  -DgroupId=es.listabl \
  -DartifactId=listabl.es \
  -Dversion=1.0-SNAPSHOT

2.3 Import to IDE
2.3.1 Eclipse

mvn eclipse:eclipse

2.4 Run

mvn jetty:run
